Oh, maksudmu mendengarkan
omong kosongmu, kan?

00:11:33.400 --> 00:11:35.280
Titu, kumohon!  - Tolong, Dimpy!

00:11:36.440 --> 00:11:38.600
Anda menyakitiku!

